Interface SessionManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SokoSessionManager

    public interface SessionManager
    Author:
    Isan Rivkin and Daniel Hake Stores all the sessions and manages them. Every communication with a session from outside is only via this session manager class used with unique sessionID.
